		<article>
				<h1>building a static userspace</h1>
				<p>date: 2013.11.18</p>
				<p>/etc/portage/make.conf:</p>
			   <p class="code">[...]
USE="${USE} static static-libs"
[...]</p>
				<p>Setting above USE-flags and trying to compile as much as possible with them is all I'm capable of right now.</p>
				<br>
				<h2>Why building a static userspace?</h2>
				<p><a href="http://sta.li/faq">That's why.</a> And for fun.</p>
				<br>
				<h2>This is a list of packages which <u>fail</u> to build:</h2>
			   <p class="code">=app-arch/tar-1.27-r2
=net-misc/wget-1.14</p>
				<p><u>Logs and build-info</u> of failed builds can be found <a href="https://cosmofox.net/DL/Gen2/Static/failed/">here</a>.</p>
